FastAPI Development Command
Run:
            fastapi dev main.py
            http://127.0.0.1:8000
The `fastapi dev` command starts the development server and automatically reloads the application when source files change.
Method 2: Uvicorn Command
You can also run:
            uvicorn main:app --reload
Do not use automatic reload as a production deployment configuration.

